Gesture-Based Actions
Quick Contribute: Swipe right on any active group card to sign and submit a transaction.

Instant Settlement: Powered by Stellar for real-time balance updates and second-speed settlement.

Secure Signing: Biometric confirmation triggers automatically after your gesture is completed.

Transparent History: Tap to view all past contributions and payouts directly on the ledger.

Key Interaction
Quick Action: Swipe right to reveal payment actions; biometric authentication follows immediately.
